            <h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">En&nbsp;</span><font color="#0645ad" face="sans-serif"><span style="background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">matemáticas</span></font><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">, concretamente en&nbsp;</span><font color="#0645ad" face="sans-serif"><span style="background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">aritmética</span></font><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">, se dice que un&nbsp;</span><font color="#0645ad" face="sans-serif"><span style="background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">número entero</span></font><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">&nbsp;</span><i style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">b</i><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">&nbsp;es&nbsp;</span><b style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">divisible</b><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">&nbsp;entre otro entero&nbsp;</span><i style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">a</i><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">&nbsp;(no nulo) si existe un entero&nbsp;</span><i style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">c</i><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">&nbsp;tal que:&nbsp;</span><span class="mwe-math-element" style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle b=a\cdot c}"><semantics><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle b=a\cdot c}</annotation></semantics></math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/260dcca02c4512fe20673fcf984737a2f91a3ebe" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" alt="{\displaystyle b=a\cdot c}" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 8.012ex; height: 2.176ex;"></span><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">. Esto es equivalente a decir que el&nbsp;</span><font color="#0645ad" face="sans-serif"><span style="background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">resto</span></font><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">&nbsp;de la&nbsp;</span><font color="#0645ad" face="sans-serif"><span style="background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">división euclídea</span></font><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">&nbsp;es cero o simbólicamente&nbsp;</span><span class="mwe-math-element" style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle b-a\cdot c=0}"><semantics><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle b-a\cdot c=0}</annotation></semantics></math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/eda28168be41bf92104d846d6a31a8b169e4932f" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" alt="{\displaystyle b-a\cdot c=0}" style="vertical-align: -0.505ex; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 12.015ex; height: 2.343ex;"></span><span style="color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;">.</span><br></h4>
